My assumption with the damage bonus was that if you scored a hit at all, you got the bonus damage from the primary hand: <br>
<br>
IE: Level 42, weilding BAH I have a damage bonus of 11 (or 13, man I should really know this).<br>
<br>
So if I hit at all, the least damage I can do is 11.  This doesn't seem to be the case though, and I still occasionally see an 8 so flutter by.  Not in the runejustended kind of fight, but in every day battle.<br>
