It kicks in when your lvl 53+ and works for primary hand only.  Your not gonna see it at lvl 43 and you have to wait till 53+.  Once youre mid 50's or so, you'll land a critical attack.  Its got a number in parenthasis like this (63).  If you check your damage message, it should say something like hits for 66.  Thus your damage bonus is 3 [66-63=3].  Thats the bonus you get for every swing, and it goes up in lvl.<br>
<br>
