<br>
Check out the faq for the formula, but basically the 1h damage bonus scales up from 1 at level 27 or 28 to 11 at 60.  The 2h bonus is a little more complicated because it depends both on level and on weapon delay.  It only affects your primary hand weapon.  So your bonus will be a lot higher with a 150 delay weapon than with say a 30 delay weapon.  Ignore the damage bonus listed on the weapons at Allakhazams and such because not all of them were posted by level 60s so they will be the bonus at whatever level the poster was at. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=85547>Khumak</a><br>
