<br>
You used to get the global critical hit message, then the personal hit message blow it. These were not the same number. The final hit was a point greater back then. (damage bonus is added AFTER the crit too, this means) You don't see this now because they changed the crit message to show final damage.<br>
<br>
How did I know this was only on my mainhand? I used a 1hb main and a 1hs off. The bonus only showed up on the crits done by crushing. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=91801">Wychway Darkmink</a><BR>Inky Warlady, Bristlebane<BR><br>Facts:<br>1. Minks are mammals.<br> 
